  title `The Coal India (Regulation of Transfers and Validation) Act, 2000`
  actNumber (45)
  enactmentDate 2000-12-08
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/1990`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `कोल इंडिया (अन्तरणों का विनियमन औरविधिमान्यकरण) अधिनियम, 2000`
  actYear (2000)
  ministry `Ministry of Coal`
  longTitle `An Act to empower the Central Government to direct the transfer of the land, or of the rights in or over land or of the right, title and interest in relation to a coal mine, coking coal mine or coke oven plant, vested in the Coal India Limited or in a subsidiary company to any subsidiary company of Coal India Limited or any other subsidiary company and to validate certain transfers of such land or rights.`
  enforcementDate 08-12-2000
  fetchedAt `2026-05-08T19:40:54.962Z`
  translations obj_root_law_translations
