obj_root_law_sections_1:
  sectionId (30841)
  sectionNo (1)
  orderNo 1
  title `Short title.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_1_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_8_8_00007_200045_1517807324022&sectionId=30841&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_8_8_00007_200045_1517807324022
obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `This Act may be called the Coal India (Regulation of Transfers and Validation) Act,`
  line 2000.
obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (30842)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title Definitions.
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_8_8_00007_200045_1517807324022&sectionId=30842&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_8_8_00007_200045_1517807324022
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires,--`
  line
  line `(a) "Coal India" means the Coal India Limited, a Government company incorporated under the`
  line `Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956) having its registered office at Calcutta and includes its predecessor`
  line `Government company, namely, the Coal Mines Authority Limited;`
  line
  line `(b) "subsidiary company" means the following subsidiary companies of Coal India, namely:--`
  line
  line `(i) the Central Coal Fields Limited, Ranchi and includes its predecessor Government`
  line `company, namely, the National Coal Development Corporation Limited, Ranchi;`
  line
  line `(ii) the Bharat Coking Coal Limited, Dhanbad;`
  line
  line `(iii) the Western Coal Fields Limited, Nagpur;`
  line
  line `(iv) the Eastern Coal Fields Limited, Sanctoria;`
  line
  line `(v) the Central Mine Planning and Design Institute Limited, Ranchi;`
  line
  line `(vi) the South-Eastern Coal Fields Limited, Bilaspur;`
  line
  line `(vii) the Northern Coal Fields Limited, Singrauli;`
  line
  line `(viii) the Mahanadi Coal Fields Limited, Sambalpur;`
  line
  line `and includes such other subsidiary company of Coal India as may be incorporated under the`
  line `Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956) from time to time;`
  line
  line `(c) words and expressions used herein and not defined but defined in the Coking Coal Mines`
  line `(Nationalisation) Act, 1972 (36 of 1972) or the Coal Mines (Nationalisation) Act, 1973 (26 of 1973),`
  line `shall have the meanings, respectively, assigned to them in those Acts.`
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_3:
  sectionId (30843)
  sectionNo (3)
  orderNo 3
  title `Power of Central Government to direct transfer of land, rights, title or interest.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_3_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_8_8_00007_200045_1517807324022&sectionId=30843&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_8_8_00007_200045_1517807324022
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line `(1)`
  line `Notwithstanding anything contained in any other law for the time being in force, the Central Government`
  line `may, if it is satisfied that a subsidiary company is willing to comply, or has complied, with such terms`
  line `and conditions as that Government think fit to impose, direct, by notification in the Official Gazette, that`
  line `the land or rights in or over such land or the right, title and interest in relation to a coal mine, coking coal`
  line `mine or a coke over plant vested in the Coal India shall, instead of continuing to vest in the Coal India,`
  line `vest in that subsidiary company or, where such land or right, title or interest vests in subsidiary company,`
  line `in another subsidiary company.`
  line
  line `(2) Where the land or right in or over such land or the right, title and interest in relation to a coal`
  line `mine, coking coal mine or a coke over plant vest in a subsidiary company under sub-section(1), such`
  line `subsidiary company shall, on and from the date of such vesting, be deemed to have become the lessee in`
  line `relation to such coal mine or coking coal mine as if a fresh mining lease in relation to such coal mine or`
  line `coking coal mine had been granted to it under the Mineral Concession Rules, 1960 made under section 13 of the Mines and Minerals (Development and Regulation) Act, 1957 (67 of 1957) for the maximum`
  line `period for which such lease could have been granted under those rules, and all the rights and liabilities of`
  line `Coal India or, as the case may be, the subsidiary company in relation to such coal mine or coking coal`
  line `mine shall, on and from the date of such vesting, be deemed to have become the rights and liabilities,`
  line `respectively, of subsidiary company first-mentioned.`
obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_4:
  sectionId (30844)
  sectionNo (4)
  orderNo 4
  title `Validation of certain transfers.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_4_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_8_8_00007_200045_1517807324022&sectionId=30844&sectionno=4&orderno=4&orgactid=AC_CEN_8_8_00007_200045_1517807324022
obj_root_law_sections_4_content:
  string
  line `A subsidiary company which was operating, or was in control`
  line `of, any coal mine, coking coal mine, or coke oven plant which was vested in the Coal India or any other`
  line `subsidiary company immediately before the commencement of this Act, shall be deemed to have been`
  line `vested with the land or rights in or over such land or the right, title and interest in relation to such coal`
  line `mine, coking coal mine or coke oven plant and such vesting shall be deemed to have been valid and`
  line `effective at all material times as if a direction had been made by the Central Government under`
  line `sub-section (1) of section 3 and accordingly no suit or other proceeding shall be instituted, maintained or`
  line `continued in any court on the ground that such subsidiary company was not competent to operate or`
  line `control such coal mine, coking coal mine or coke oven plant.`
obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_translations:
  hi obj_root_law_translations_hi
